GuiGenericMain
public class GenericMain
extends java.awt.Frame
implements java.lang.Runnable

This is a generic test program for exercising a show file. It accepts commands to boss the show around on stdin. Probably more interesting is the subclass of this, GuiGenericMain. This command-line version came first, but I pretty quickly got tired of it and made the GUI instead.
